{{flavour|Draws searing flames from lava. Any enemies of the caster standing next to or above lava will be burned.}}

'''Pyroclastic Surge''' is a monster-only spell which deals pure [[fire]] damage to all enemies on or adjacent to a [[lava]] tile.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Pyroclastic Surge was added in [[0.27]].

